    "title": "微信接入",
    "author": "hua",
    "updateDate": 1490155632351,
    "content": "<h1><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">微信接入</span><br/></h1><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"></span></p><hr/><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 14px;\">您已拥有一个通过微信认证的微信公众号，只需将您的微信公众号绑定到微上客云客服系统，就可以轻松处理来自微信网友的咨询。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 14px;\">注意：（<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">未通过微信认证的服务号或订阅号无法使用微上客云客服的完整功能。使用微上客云客服时，微信多客服即停止使用，并关闭多客服客户端上的自动回复功能。</span>）</span></strong></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">第</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">步：注册微上客云客服账号</span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span></p><hr/><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">在微上客客服注册页面，填写您的邮箱、密码等信息，注册微上客账号。</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-2-2-1.png\"></span></span></span></p><h2><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">第2步：绑定微信公众号</span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span></p><hr/><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、登陆微上客，进入<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“管理员模式”</span>&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">渠道管理</span>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">添加消息渠道</span>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">点击微信</span>logo<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，添加微信公众账号</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-2-2-2.png\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">、点击</span><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">点击进入扫码</span><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">，进入微信公众平台，扫描二维码授权微上客平台。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-2-2-3.png\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">、扫码授权即可</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-2-2-4.png\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">第</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">步：设置微信渠道</span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span></p><hr/><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">登陆微上客进入<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“管理员模式”</span>&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">渠道管理</span>&nbsp;&gt; 选择微信渠道</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">您可以设置微信渠道工作时间，渠道最大进线量，首次关注欢迎语<br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">排队等待回复语等</span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span><br/></p><h2><br/></h2><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>"
}